<p>Ester was driving home from work two days ago when she saw a <a href="http://mikesautoglassfl.com/">Mike‚Äôs Auto Glass</a> van. What jumped out at her was the ‚Äú<strong>Specializing in RV Glass</strong>‚Äù. She called me and I jumped on their <a href="http://mikesautoglassfl.com/">website</a>. I filled out the online estimator.</p>

<p>Within an hour they called to get more information. I told them what we have, which always is a bit of a story. You can‚Äôt say it is a truck, and when you say school bus you must explain it is no long acting as a school bus. They said they would call back with an estimate.</p>

