<p>Because the glass is flat they cut new glass right in the driveway. They used the old glass as a template. After the glass was cut they used a sander to smooth off the edges. The guy doing the work said he didn‚Äôt want to be filmed so we had to take pictures sparingly and in stealth mode.</p>

